Primal Remedy<br>
<br>
 Level: 44  <br>
Target: Pet Only <br>
Range: 100 <br>
Cast Time: 4.0 seconds <br>
Recast Time: 7.5 seconds <br>
Duration: 30 seconds <br>
Mana Cost: 200 <br>
<br>
Effect:<br>
<br>
<br>
Heal 80 points of damage every 6 seconds<br>
<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Elemental Empathy<br>
<br>
 Level: 52  <br>
Target: Pet Only <br>
Range: 100 <br>
Cast Time: 6 seconds <br>
Recast Time: 12 seconds <br>
Duration: 90 minutes <br>
Mana Cost: 300 <br>
<br>
 Effect (on pet):<br>
<br>
<br>
60% haste <br>
+60 strength <br>
+20 armor class<br>
 <br>
 <br>
 Effect (on caster):<br>
<br>
<br>
+280 to maximum hit points <br>
+105 armor class <br>
+30 magic resistance<br>
 <br>
