<br>
So it appears they gave low 50s mages, a spell that combines the shielding (nearly exactly the same hps, ac, and mana as 54 shield spell), and burnout (same haste) in a 1.5 hour long buff so they only cast 1 spell every 1.5 hours instead of 2 and one being recast every 15 mins<br>
<br>
so this spell does nothing, absolutely nothing for anyone with a 60+ shield spell, OR burnout 5, so instead of coming our top level spells so it could be useful, they combined mid level stuff to make it completely craptastic<br>
<br>
I'm seriously considering canceling my pre order, I can't believe they call this an expansion (extension, whatever) and expect us to pay about the same price we payed for all the others. Those spells were put together in about 10 minutes, max, and offer nothing, no classes offer anything to a character over 55 or so. then they throw 5 zones at us, that aren't even designed with a single one in mind for 60+ people.<br>
<br>
I'm so uterly disgusted at sony right now... I just realized exactly why they put the spells on the last day, so a lot of people will have bought expansion and less with not buy/cancel if they only have a couple days notice at the end, and we've already been lured in by wonderful things like changing our robe color (woot!)<br>
